thread.title: Gazans bury their dead on 'Nakba day'

title: Gazans bury their dead on 'Nakba day'
text:
Gazans bury their dead on 'Nakba day' 12:28pm EDT - 01:36
Gazans buried their dead after the Palestinians' bloodiest day for years, when Israeli forces opened fire on protesters angered by the new U.S. embassy in Jerusalem. Lucy Fielder reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
